## Get Specific Champion [/champions/{champion}]

### /champions/{champion} [GET]

Returns info for a specific champion

+ Parameters
    + champion - champion name in all lower case no spaces


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        "example": [
            {
                "rankedPlayEnabled": true,
                "botEnabled": false,
                "botMmEnabled": false,
                "active": true,
                "freeToPlay": false,
                "id": "Champion1",
                "recommended" : 
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "count": 1,
                            "id": 3112
                        },
                        {
                            "count": 1,
                            "id": 1001
                        },
                        {
                            "count": 3,
                            "id": 2003
                        }
                    ],
                "active": true
            }
        ]
        
