## Game Mode [/gameModes/{gameMode}]
    
### /gameModes/{gameMode} [GET]

Return info for a game mode

+ Parameter
    + gameMode - String game mode all lower case, using dashes instead of space
    
+ Response 200 (applicaton/json)
    
        "example" : [
            "The Dark Star Rises": {
                "FunLevel": "Not Very",
                "Playable Champions" : "Thresh",
                "Items": [],
                "SummonerSpells": []
            }, 
            "Summoners Rift": {
                "etc": "..."
            }
        ]
 
 
 
 
        
