## Summoner's Match History [/summoner/matchHistory/{summonerName}]

### /summoner/matchHistory/{summonerName} [GET]

Returns recent match history for a summoner

+ Parameter 
    + summonerName - fetch match history for this specific summoner
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    
        "matches" : [
            {
                "lane": "MID",
                "gameId": 2606708491,
                "champion": 60,
                "platformId": "NA1",
                "timestamp": 1506408727763,
                "queue": 65,
                "role": "NONE",
                "season": 9
            },
            {
                "lane": "MID",
                "gameId": 2606706891,
                "champion": 1,
                "platformId": "NA1",
                "timestamp": 1506406702009,
                "queue": 2,
                "role": "SOLO",
                "season": 9
            },
            {
                "etc...", 1234
            }
        ]

## Match Details [/matches/matchHistory/{matchID}]

### /matches/matchHistory/{matchID} [GET]

Fetches details about a specific match.

+ Parameter
    + matchID - ID of the match you are looking up

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    
        "example": [
            "timestamp": 33,
            "participantFrames": {
                "1": {
                    "totalGold": 1400,
                    "teamScore": 0,
                    "participantId": 1,
                    "level": 1,
                    "currentGold": 1400,
                    "minionsKilled": 0,
                    "dominionScore": 0,
                    "position": {
                        "y": 1180,
                        "x": 1103
                    },
                    "xp": 0,
                    "jungleMinionsKilled": 0
                },
                "2": {
                    "etc..." : 0
                }
            }
        ]